                                    <div class="top">
                                        
                                            <div class="description collapse"><p>With the growth in the number of agent nodes, maintaining a database and the history of node configuration and metadata is crucial for any infrastructure. PuppetDB helps to maintain this database and also aids in configuration via exported resources.</p><ul>
							<li> Install and configure the PostgreSQL database </li>
							<li> Install and configure the PuppetDB, and connect it to the PostgreSQL database </li>
							<li> Integrate PuppetDB with Puppet server&nbsp;</li></ul></div>
                                        
