                                <div class="left-content">
                                    <span class="udi udi-play-circle"></span>
                                    <div class="top">
                                        
                                            <div class="description collapse"><p>After the data from thousands of nodes are stored in a database, they are not very useful, unless they can be queried and visualized using structured querying mechanisms. Different Puppet query mechanisms and dashboards helps in solving these problems.</p><ul>
							<li> Configure workstation, and understand methods to query PuppetDB </li>
							<li> Understand PuppetDB API endpoints and perform queries. </li>
							<li> Use default PuppetDB dashboard for visualization&nbsp;</li></ul></div>
                                        
